Package: absSimSeq
Title: RNA-Seq Simulation with Absolute Counts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Warren", "McGee", email = "warren.a.mcg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Warren McGee [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Warren McGee <warren.a.mcg@gmail.com>
Description: This package extends the polyester
  package by simulating an RNA-Seq using absolute RNA counts before
  converting the result into relative proportions (in TPMs and expected
  fragments) that are then used as input for polyester.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Imports:
   biomaRt,
   Biostrings,
   data.table,
   DESeq2,
   dplyr,
   methods,
   polyester,
   parallel,
   sleuth,
   sleuthALR,
   stats,
   truncnorm
